{"tid":2314391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★投訴 iPhone 12信號差  連打電話也不能！Apple：轉台以解決問題","createTime":"2020-12-06T13:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T13:41:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a94b4aec552ef2e00851a86919596fbc9b8f4fbb","tid":2314391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"Apple 最新的 iPhone 12 系列，除採用 A14 晶片外，其力推的賣點應是支援 5G 網絡，不過，有不少 iPhone 12 用家表示其新電話的信號相當差，不但無法使用 5G 網絡，連打電話也成問題。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n近日 Reddit 討論區不乏投訴 iPhone 12 信號差的討論串，用戶們表示，其 iPhone 12 經常在 5G 、4G 兩者頻密自動切換，甚至出現過斷網、無信號的情況，更嚴重者連 Wi-Fi 也無法連接，要重新啟動電話才可以正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n而除了上網問題，有用戶表示打電話也會間歇性出現障礙，有時候需要步出房外才可收到信號，但使用同樣電訊商 Sim 卡的 Android 電話就沒有相關問題。<br />\n<br />\n有用戶曾向電訊商投訴求助，而電訊商 職員只回應指是 iPhone 問題，但 Apple 售後服務就轉而指是電訊商問題，甚至喚有相關問題的用戶更換電訊商以處理相關情況，似乎各 iPhone 12 用家距離真正解決問題可謂遙遙無期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/06/iphone-12-signal/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F06%2Fiphone-12-signal%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=8a6c6ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/06/iphone-12-signal/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"e6229cd8b7fb780cda4148ef02e893a833c3d03e","tid":2314391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1b4e33962b3a63d805055e59da3a28ae0f3063","tid":2314391,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"已支化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}